{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3d6b906958","title":"对全国文联和所属各协会整风的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"109072580b","index":0,"year":1964,"month":6,"day":27,"articleId":"3d6b906958"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"afe10bb6f7","type":"title","text":"对全国文联和所属各协会整风的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"3d6b906958"},{"id":"612d8d1ce0","type":"paragraph","text":"这些协会和他们所掌握的刊物的大多数（据说有少数几个好的），十五年来，基本上（不是一切人）不执行党的政策，做官当老爷，不去接近工农兵，不去反映社会主义革命和建设。最近几年，竟然跌到了修正主义的边缘。如不认真改造，势必在将来的某一天，要变成像匈牙利裴多菲俱乐部那样的团体。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"3d6b906958"}],"page":{"id":"6809511322","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"3d6b906958","start":268,"end":268}}}},"__N_SSG":true}